source.name: Property Tax Rates
source.description: Each tax roll year, the Alameda County Auditor has published a hardcopy Tax Rates book.  This table has the detail data used to create the book.  The tax rates are shown for each Fund within a Tax Rate Area where the rate is not zero.  This table contains data from 2005 to the current tax year.
